it's locals only.

09:59.933 --> 10:02.634
<i> But it brings out some of</i>
<i> the best fishermen in kona.</i>

10:03.637 --> 10:04.936
You saying I'm a local now?

10:04.938 --> 10:06.404
You got the tattoo.

10:06.406 --> 10:07.939
I got the tattoo.

10:08.041 --> 10:09.774
And I'm with you, right?

10:09.776 --> 10:11.810
-Casey.
-[man] casey.

10:11.812 --> 10:14.546
Yeah. I am with silva,
jeff silva.

10:14.615 --> 10:17.248
[man] all right, gentlemen,
it's a two-person minimum.

10:17.317 --> 10:18.550
Sign in, please.

10:18.619 --> 10:19.651
[jeff] <i> the rules are simple</i>

10:19.720 --> 10:20.952
The crew with the most meat
on the boat

10:20.954 --> 10:22.921
After two days
of fishing wins.

10:22.923 --> 10:24.756
<i> Everybody gets to keep</i>
<i> what they catch,</i>

10:24.858 --> 10:26.091
So while it's good networking,

10:26.093 --> 10:27.325
<i> We can also punch out</i>
<i> the order</i>

10:27.327 --> 10:28.426
<i> With taylor in kauai.</i>

10:29.429 --> 10:31.129
[man] hold on to your receipt.
Good luck.

10:31.131 --> 10:32.130
[casey] thank you.

10:32.532 --> 10:33.565
Take care, guys.

10:35.402 --> 10:37.135
So where do
you wanna start fishing?

10:37.204 --> 10:38.903
Let's just make our way out
and start heading down,

10:38.905 --> 10:40.639
And try to get
in front of everybody,

10:40.740 --> 10:41.840
And just go from there.

10:41.908 --> 10:42.840
Okay.

10:42.842 --> 10:44.009
Oh, there's kalina and keoni
right there.

10:44.011 --> 10:45.510
Oh, nice. Let's go say hi.

10:46.780 --> 10:47.912
Hi guys.

10:47.914 --> 10:49.214
Hey. Good morning there, jeff.

10:49.216 --> 10:50.048
How you guys doing?

10:50.050 --> 10:51.249
-Good. How are you?
-Good.

10:51.318 --> 10:53.251
Thanks for having us down.
This is casey.

10:53.320 --> 10:55.053
-Hi, I'm kalina.
-Casey, this is kalina,
this is keoni.

10:55.055 --> 10:56.321
-Nice to meet you.
-This is her tournament.

10:56.323 --> 10:57.522
I just wanna introduce
you guys.

10:57.524 --> 10:58.390
Nice to meet you.

10:58.458 --> 10:59.824
-Yeah. Yeah.
-So thanks for having us.

10:59.826 --> 11:01.526
Super stoked.

11:01.528 --> 11:02.927
Where are you guys
gonna go today?

11:02.929 --> 11:03.928
Probably gonna head
down south.

11:03.930 --> 11:04.929
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

11:04.931 --> 11:06.031
Heard there's some action
down there, so.

11:06.033 --> 11:07.799
[jeff] just you two today?

11:07.801 --> 11:08.733
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

11:08.735 --> 11:10.001
My dad, uh, was supposed
to go with us,

11:10.003 --> 11:11.302
But he had to stay back,

11:11.304 --> 11:12.804
One of my cooks
didn't make it in, so...

11:12.806 --> 11:13.871
-[jeff] oh, no way.
-Yeah.

11:13.940 --> 11:15.306
He's not fishing
with us today unfortunately.

11:15.308 --> 11:16.341
So, it's just me and kalina.

11:16.410 --> 11:17.275
All right.

11:17.277 --> 11:18.309
You're his ace
in the hole anyway,

